OL,3,CBiden partially lifts ban on Ukraine
OL,4,Cusing US weapons to strike Russia
OL,6,FPresident has given Ukraine the green
OL,7,Flight to use US weaponry to strike
OL,8,Finside Russia for the limited purpose
OL,9,Fof defending Kharkiv, according to US
OL,10,Fofficials familiar with the matter.
OL,12,FThe officials, who requested
OL,13,Fanonymity, underscored that the policy
OL,14,Fcalling on Ukraine not to use US-
OL,15,Fprovided long-range missiles and other
OL,16,Fmunitions to strike inside Russia
OL,17,Foffensively has not changed.
