OL,3,CBiden partially lifts ban on Ukraine
OL,4,Cusing US weapons to strike Russia
OL,6,FThe move comes as Ukrainian officials
OL,7,Fhave stepped up calls on the US
OL,8,Fadministration to allow its forces to
OL,9,Fdefend itself against attacks
OL,10,Foriginating from Russian territory.
OL,12,Fhas recently intensified attacks on
OL,13,FKharkiv, Ukraine's second-largest
OL,14,Fcity, which is just 20 kilometres (12
OL,15,Fmiles) from the Russian border.
