OL,3,CBiden partially lifts ban on Ukraine
OL,4,Cusing US weapons to strike Russia
OL,6,FThe assault came after Russia amassed
OL,7,F30,000 troops across the border from
OL,8,Fthe Ukrainian city. Almost 8,000 local
OL,9,Fpeople were forced to evacuate their
OL,10,Fhomes as Russia began to shell the
OL,11,Fcity and breach the border.
OL,13,FRussia are unlikely to capture
OL,14,FKharkiv, but its advance has compelled
OL,15,FUkraine to send more troops to the
OL,16,Fregion, leaving other areas more
OL,17,Fvulnerable to attack.
