OL,3,CBiden partially lifts ban on Ukraine
OL,4,Cusing US weapons to strike Russia
OL,6,F's army pushed the Kremlin's forces
OL,7,Fout of Kharkiv in the autumn of 2022,
OL,8,Frecapturing the region seven months
OL,9,Fafter Russia's full-scale invasion.
OL,11,FSince the start of the Russian
OL,12,Finvasion in February 2022, Biden has
OL,13,Fbeen steadfast in his opposition to
OL,14,Fthe Ukrainians using American-made
OL,15,Fweaponry offensively - out of concern
OL,16,Fit could lead to Moscow widening the
OL,17,Fwar.
